snippet.title: Integration between Databricks and Microsoft | Govern, secure and integrate your data
snippet.description:
Databricks CEO, Ali Ghodsi, and EVP of Cloud and AI at Microsoft, Scott Guthrie, on the Databricks x Microsoft partnership and how it enables customers to leverage their data.  

How the Databricks Microsoft partnership helps organizations drive business outcomes with AI.
